items.title: House narrowly passes Trump's megabill in major victory for Republicans
items.description: President Donald Trump worked the phones late into the night to help House Republican leadership deliver his second-term policy agenda.

items.title: Trump speaks with Putin after U.S. pauses some weapons shipments to Ukraine
items.description: The Trump-Putin call comes after the U.S. said it would halt some weapons shipments to Ukraine, which continues to fight off invading Russian forces.

items.title: Trump's megabill is in real trouble, as House GOP defectors vote 'no' on advancing it

items.title: Trump says U.S. struck trade deal with Vietnam that imposes 20% tariff on its imports
items.description: Vietnam, whose exports to the U.S. reportedly comprised 30% of its gross domestic product last year, is especially vulnerable to Trump's tariffs.

items.title: Senate sets record for longest vote-a-rama as Trump's 'big, beautiful bill' teeters
items.description: Senators worked through the night on amendments to President Donald Trump's "big, beautiful" spending bill. A final vote could come Tuesday.
